    "Though these attributes are not related to the whole system but focus on the explanation presentation only, they impact users' perception, as our findings revealed.",
    "These attributes are concise, nontechnical information, categorical information representation, local explanation, and controlled information flow.",
    "Later, the study participants stated that using XAI for recommendations would give them a comprehensive idea of the system's decision-making, increasing transparency and trust in the social media platform.",
    "Also, the explanation can impact their perceived bias regarding the system, as we have seen in our findings.",
    "These factors can help lay users' social media usage experience."
